frames.caption: A vintage steam locomotive chugs through a dense forest, surrounded by autumn foliage. Thick plumes of smoke billow from its chimney, contrasting with the warm hues of the leaves. The train's headlights shine brightly, illuminating the path ahead.
frames.description: The scene captures a historic steam train traveling through a forest during autumn. The vibrant orange and brown leaves create a picturesque backdrop, enhancing the nostalgic feel of the locomotive's journey.
